        "action": "Refund all or part of citizenship fees when an application is rejected",
        "additional_details": "The fee is too high for it to be acceptable for the Government to reject an application and keep these fees. The Government should refund all or part of citizenship fees when an application is rejected.",
        "background": "I've recently been refused citizenship after paying fees of \u00a31269. I believe that it is unfair for citizenship fees to kept in full when an application is rejected.",
